## 5. Interactions & Workflows

### 5.1 User Types in Search

```
User Input: "15 pro"
→ searchQuery state updated
→ useMemo re-runs filter
→ filteredParts re-computed
→ Grid re-renders (instant, no network call)
```

### 5.2 User Adds to Cart

```
User clicks "Add to Cart"
→ handleAddToCart(part) invoked
→ TODO: Dispatch to cart context/Zustand store
→ TODO: Validate MOQ (5 units minimum)
→ TODO: Show toast notification
→ Currently: logs to console + alert()
```

### 5.3 Network Failure

```
Component mounts
→ fetch('/api/parts') fails (network error, 500, malformed response)
→ setState({ error: "...", loading: false })
→ Error UI rendered
→ User clicks "Retry" → window.location.reload()
```

