## 10. Testing Strategy

### Unit Tests (Jest)

```typescript
// Filter logic
it('filters parts by brand', () => {
  const parts = [{ brand: 'Apple', ... }, { brand: 'Samsung', ... }];
  // Assert only Apple parts returned when activeBrand='Apple'
});

it('filters by AND logic', () => {
  const part = { searchIndex: 'iphone 15 pro screen' };
  // "15 screen" → match ✓
  // "15 ipad" → no match ✗
});
```

### Integration Tests (Playwright)

```typescript
it('loads parts and allows search', async ({ page }) => {
  await page.goto('/catalog');
  await expect(page.locator('[aria-label="Search"]')).toBeFocused();
  await page.fill('[aria-label="Search"]', '15 pro');
  const results = await page.locator('[data-testid="part-card"]').count();
  expect(results).toBeGreaterThan(0);
});
```

