## 11. Known Limitations & Future Work

|Item                    |Priority|Notes                                                            |
|------------------------|--------|-----------------------------------------------------------------|
|**Server-side search**  |High    |For catalogs > 10K parts, implement pagination + server filtering|
|**Cart integration**    |High    |Replace `handleAddToCart` stub with real Zustand/Context dispatch|
|**Typeahead**           |Medium  |Suggest popular searches, common part types                      |
|**Filters beyond brand**|Medium  |Add facets: Quality (OEM/Aftermarket), Price range, Stock status |
|**Saved searches**      |Low     |Let users bookmark favorite searches (localStorage → DB)         |
|**Export to CSV**       |Low     |Download filtered results for bulk operations                    |
|**Advanced sort**       |Low     |Sort by price, stock, relevance (default: relevance)             |

